    "shortDescription": "<p>This spell functions like @Compendium[pf1.spells.w6bdfme0t8frk73p]{animal aspect}, except you can either gain two aspects at once or one aspect that adds effects to the aspects that <em>animal aspect</em> grants, as described below. <br><em>Frog</em>: You gain a Swim speed equal to half your normal speed, and all the benefits of having a swim speed. <br><em>Gorilla</em>: You gain a +2 competence bonus on @UUID[Compendium.pf1.pf1e-rules.x175kVqUfLGPt8tC.JournalEntryPage.2h6hz5AkTDxKPFxr]{Perception} checks, and a +1 competence bonus on Fortitude saves. <br><em>Monkey</em>: You gain a +4 competence bonus on @UUID[Compendium.pf1.pf1e-rules.x175kVqUfLGPt8tC.JournalEntryPage.gGfJO90ZuRT4sZ9X]{Acrobatics} checks. <br><em>Otter</em>: Your swim speed increases to your full normal speed, and you need not make concentration checks to cast spells underwater. <br><em>Raccoon</em>: Your competence bonuses on @UUID[Compendium.pf1.pf1e-rules.x175kVqUfLGPt8tC.JournalEntryPage.cSdUATLHBFfw3v4s]{Disable Device}, @UUID[Compendium.pf1.pf1e-rules.x175kVqUfLGPt8tC.JournalEntryPage.joza8kAIiImrPft7]{Sleight of Hand}, and @UUID[Compendium.pf1.pf1e-rules.x175kVqUfLGPt8tC.JournalEntryPage.wRWHk7tCUHR99PzD]{Stealth} checks increase to +4. <br><em>Raptor</em>: Your enhancement bonus to speed increases to +30 feet, and you gain the benefit of the @Compendium[pf1.feats.bXeW4kLCErPBFpNB]{Run} feat. <br><em>Tree Lizard</em>: You gain a +4 competence bonus on @UUID[Compendium.pf1.pf1e-rules.x175kVqUfLGPt8tC.JournalEntryPage.wRWHk7tCUHR99PzD]{Stealth} checks.</p>"
